data.description: Calling all fishermen, or just lake lovers in general.  Experience serene lakeside living in this exquisite log home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with a large wrap around porch.  Savor your morning coffee with unparalled views of the tranquil lake, making every moment a picturesque retreat.  In the evenings, the large porch invites you to host cookouts and family gatherings, making memories for everyone. This home is situated on five lots, so there is plenty of room for your outdoor activities as well!
